<emphasis box="[284,513,1495,1519]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="393">Lestica robustispinosa</emphasis>
Yue &amp; Ma
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[643,725,1496,1519]" pageId="2" pageNumber="393" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, Holotype ♀. a. Habitus, dorsal view. b. Head, frontal view. c. Head, dorsal view. d. Mesosoma, dorsal view. e. Mesosternum. f. Hind leg. g. Fore leg. h. Fore wing. i. Pygidial plate, dorsal view. j. Metasoma, dorsal view. Scale bar = 1 mm.
</paragraph>
